d 'LOGOUTE': module to provide automated table conversion to HTML, Markdown, and LaTeX
d
d	logoute is built on top of logout (logout.ado by Roy Wada).
d It keeps the original table-capture	 workflow from logout and
d adds direct HTML/Markdown table export, so users can generate   
d publish-ready HTML tables from the same syntax.    It is
d particularly useful for generating descriptive statistics tables
d or simple frequency	 lists that need to be embedded in web
d reports or LaTeX documents. Compared with the    original logout,
d logoute extends functionality by exporting HTML/Markdown tables
d directly    and is optimized for the tohtml workflow, producing
d cleaner HTML with proper class    attributes for styling. 
d
d KW: data management
d KW: table conversion
d KW: HTML
d KW: Markdown
d KW: LaTeX
d
d Requires: Stata version 16
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260427
d
d Author: Kerry Du, School of Management, Xiamen University
d Support: email kerrydu@@xmu.edu.cn
d
d Author:  Huanyu Jia,  School of Business, Zhengzhou University
d Support: email jiahuanyu@@zzu.edu.cn
d
f logoute.ado
f logoute.sthlp
